#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "In addition to `EntityManager` and `EntityManagerFactory`, Quarkus also supports injecting the following JPA/Hibernate components:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
