#. type: Title ===
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "Plugging in converters and entity listeners"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "The Quarkus extension for Hibernate ORM supports injecting link:{hibernate-orm-docs-url}#basic-jpa-convert[attribute converters] and link:{hibernate-orm-docs-url}#events-jpa-callbacks[entity listeners] into Hibernate ORM."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "Just use them as you would in vanilla Hibernate ORM (see documentation linked above), and rely on CDI features (`@Inject`, `@PostConstruct`, `@PreDestroy`, ...) in the converter/listener implementation as needed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "When no CDI scope is specified, the converter/listener will behave as if it was `@Dependent` and will be instantiated once per persistence unit it's used in."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "You can force a CDI scope by annotating the converter/listener class with for example `@ApplicationScoped`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "In very exotic scenarios, if you need to prevent usage of CDI in a converter/listener even though it uses CDI annotations (`@Inject`, ...), annotate it with `@Vetoed`. The class will then be instantiated by Hibernate ORM through its default constructor."
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ===
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "Plugging in other custom components"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid ""
"The Quarkus extension for Hibernate ORM will automatically\n"
"inject components annotated with `@PersistenceUnitExtension` into Hibernate Search."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
msgid "The annotation can optionally target a specific persistence unit with `@PersistenceUnitExtension(name = \"nameOfYourPU\")`."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-orm.adoc
